Design interfaces at the quality level of modern SaaS products.

Inspiration:
Stripe
Vercel
Linear
Notion

UI principles:

- strong visual hierarchy
- card-based layout
- generous spacing
- minimal visual noise
- predictable layout patterns

Design guidelines:

Use:
- dashboard style layouts
- grouped information in cards
- grid based content structure
- clear typography hierarchy

Avoid:
- cramped layouts
- inconsistent spacing
- large blocks of undifferentiated content

Interfaces should feel modern, clean, and professional.